    <title>BIS fifth statement of new regulation: regulations covering January to June 2013</title>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;p&gt;Lists Department for Business, Innovation and Skills (&lt;abbr title="Department for Business, Innovation and Skills"&gt;BIS&lt;/abbr&gt;) measures in scope of ‘One In, Two Out’ regulations to come into force from January to June 2013, to show how &lt;abbr title="Department for Business, Innovation and Skills"&gt;BIS&lt;/abbr&gt; is removing burdens on business.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
